9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to crimes and punishments; amending
21 O.S. 2021, Section 1125, as amended by Section
11 400, Chapter 486, O.S.L. 2025 (21 O.S. Supp. 2025,
Section 1125), which relates to zones of safety;
12 expanding zone of safety to include certain places;
and providing an effective date.
